dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
This data was downloaded from the NPS website. The NPS is the data creator. Montana State Library selected all the data that exists within the State of Montana, some boundaries lie in multiple states, and maintains this dataset regularly. The NPS puts on updates as needed basis. When this updates are put out, MSL is notified and will make updates to this version.
For the full version of the data - https://irma.nps.gov/DataStore/
dataIdInfo.envirDesc: Microsoft Windows 7 Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; Esri ArcGIS 10.5.1.7333

dataLineage.statement: This data has been downloaded from the National Park Service and clipped to show all NPS Administrative Boundaries that lie within Montana. Some of these boundaries do cross into other states as well; if that is the case, the entire administrative boundary has been included in the data.
